== POWER INVERTER ==

A dc - ac power inverter is a device that converts a dc electricity to ac electricity. These inverters come in a variety of types. Modified Sine Wave or Square Wave, Quasi Square wave and True Sine Wave are a few of the models.

Most inverters are rated in watts.[http://www.4lots.com Power Inverters] are beoming more common for powering laptops, computers, tv's and other ac devices in cars and RV's. These units are also used for reliable backups during power outages.

